headline: Bolsonaro gets more than 27 years in prison for attempted coup in historic ruling
description: Four out of five justices of Brazil's Supreme Federal Court  found the former far-right president guilty. While progressive Brazilians are delighted by the verdict, some of his supporters have openly called for help from Donald Trump's America.

headline: Balenciaga returns to haute perfumery 75 years on
description: Following luxury houses such as Balmain and Valentino, Balenciaga reconnects with its olfactory heritage by unveiling a collection of 10 fragrances. These creations, contemporary interpretations of the house's refined world and the radical vision of its founder, mark the brand's ambitious comeback.

description: Although France did not come to a standstill or grind to a halt on Wednesday, numerous protests took place throughout the day across the country with large gatherings in certain cities – with headcounts between 197,000 and 250,000 people – amid the firm presence of law enforcement.
